  "detailed_description": "Photosensitivity Warning: This game features intense procedural visual effects. Space Hole 2020 features many unpredictable visual patterns and strobing lights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393310/extras/174bf620cce5d08c03e78a3f82dbba5a.poster.avif?t=1708557412\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393310/extras/174bf620cce5d08c03e78a3f82dbba5a.webm?t=1708557412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393310/extras/174bf620cce5d08c03e78a3f82dbba5a.mp4?t=1708557412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Navigate mysterious cosmic structures from different places in the entire history of reality<br></li><li> Graphics generated by overlapping unbuffered pixels<br></li><li> Play with the Freeform Machine<br></li><li> Wander and or journey from the origin of reality to the furthest reaches of technological expansion<br></li><li> \"Rewind\" and \"Restart\" keys allow instant retries and error recovery.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393310/extras/22804a2a73cf4cf5a10a8dc7e148232b.poster.avif?t=1708557412\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393310/extras/22804a2a73cf4cf5a10a8dc7e148232b.webm?t=1708557412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393310/extras/22804a2a73cf4cf5a10a8dc7e148232b.mp4?t=1708557412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Space Hole 2020 is a standalone continuation of the Space Hole games, it can be experienced independently (the games share 